<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَطَهِّرْ بَيْتِيَ لِلطَّائِفِينَ وَالْقائِمِينَ وَالرُّكَّعِ السُّجُودِ ٢٦ ١٠/ ٣٤٣.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَأَذِّنْ فِي النَّاسِ بِالْحَجِّ يَأْتُوكَ رِجالًا ... ٢٧ ٣/ ٣٩١.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أُذِنَ لِلَّذِينَ يُقاتَلُونَ بِأَنَّهُمْ ظُلِمُوا ... ٣٩ ١/ ٧١.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أُذِنَ لِلَّذِينَ يُقاتَلُونَ بِأَنَّهُمْ ... عاقِبَةُ الْأُمُورِ ٣٩- ٤١ ٩/ ٢٢٦.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَلَيَنْصُرَنَّ اللَّهُ مَنْ يَنْصُرُهُ ٤٠ ٤/ ٢١٧.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَما أَرْسَلْنا مِنْ قَبْلِكَ مِنْ رَسُولٍ وَلا نَبِيٍّ ... ٥٢ ١١/ ٢٢٨.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَيَنْسَخُ اللَّهُ ما يُلْقِي الشَّيْطانُ ٥٢ ٤/ ٢٨٢.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>يَأْتِيَهُمْ عَذابُ يَوْمٍ عَقِيمٍ ٥٥ ١٢/ ١٣٥.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لَيُدْخِلَنَّهُمْ مُدْخَلًا يَرْضَوْنَهُ ٥٩ ٤/ ٢١٧.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَجاهِدُوا فِي اللَّهِ حَقَّ جِهادِهِ ٧٨ ١٢/ ٢٠٣<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[سورة المؤمنون]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قَدْ أَفْلَحَ الْمُؤْمِنُونَ ١ ٢/ ١٩٢- ٣/ ٤٧.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَدْ أَفْلَحَ الْمُؤْمِنُونَ ... أَحْسَنُ الْخالِقِينَ ١- ١٤ ٨/ ٢٦٩.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أَخَذْنا مُتْرَفِيهِمْ بِالْعَذابِ ٦٤ ١٢/ ١٣٥.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَلَقَدْ أَخَذْناهُمْ بِالْعَذابِ فَمَا اسْتَكانُوا ٧٦ ١٢/ ٧٨.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَإِذا نُفِخَ فِي الصُّورِ فَلا أَنْسابَ ... ١٠١ ١٠/ ٢٨٣.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَفَحَسِبْتُمْ أَنَّما خَلَقْناكُمْ عَبَثاً ١١٥ ٣/ ١٥٧<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c4">[سورة النور]</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>الزَّانِيَةُ وَالزَّانِي فَاجْلِدُوا كُلَّ واحِدٍ مِنْهُما ٢ ١٠/ ١٣.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>إِنَّ الَّذِينَ جاؤُ بِالْإِفْكِ عُصْبَةٌ مِنْكُمْ ١١ ١/ ٢١٥.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>إِذْ تَلَقَّوْنَهُ بِأَلْسِنَتِكُمْ ١٥ ٤/ ٣١٩.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَتَحْسَبُونَهُ هَيِّناً وَهُوَ عِنْدَ اللَّهِ عَظِيمٌ ١٥ ١٤/ ٣٩٠.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>يَوْمَئِذٍ يُوَفِّيهِمُ اللَّهُ دِينَهُمُ الْحَقَّ ٢٥ ١٣/ ٢٤٢.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وَإِنْ تُطِيعُوهُ تَهْتَدُوا ٥٤ ٣/ ٣١٢- ٤/ ٢٠٥.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>وَعَدَ اللَّهُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا مِنْكُمْ وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحاتِ ٥٥ ٤/ ٢٢٠، ٢٣١- ٩/ ٤١- ١٤/ ١٧٩.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>إِنَّمَا الْمُؤْمِنُونَ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا بِاللَّهِ وَرَسُولِهِ ٦٢ ٣/ ١٦٧.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>وَأَقِيمُوا الصَّلاةَ وَآتُوا الزَّكاةَ ... ٥٦ ١١/ ٩<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>